  <h2 id="who-we-are">1. Who We Are</h2>
  <p>Custom Cleaning RVA ("we," "us," or "our") is a residential cleaning service based in Richmond, Virginia. Our website is located at <strong>RVACustomCleaning.com</strong>. For questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:customcleaningrva@gmail.com">customcleaningrva@gmail.com</a> or <a href="tel:8048145491">(804) 814-5491</a>.</p>

  <h2 id="information-collected">2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>Information You Provide Directly</h3>
  <p>When you submit a booking request, contact form, or newsletter signup on our website, we collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Name</strong> — to address you and identify your booking</li>
    <li><strong>Phone number</strong> — to confirm appointments and send service reminders via SMS/text</li>
    <li><strong>Email address</strong> — to send booking confirmations, appointment reminders, and (with your opt-in consent) newsletters and promotions</li>
    <li><strong>Home address</strong> — so our cleaning team knows where to go</li>
    <li><strong>Service preferences and notes</strong> — e.g., pets in the home, entry codes, cleaning preferences</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
  <p>When you visit our website, standard web server logs may record your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time of visit. We may use cookies or similar tools to improve your website experience. We do not use tracking for advertising purposes.</p>

  <h2 id="how-we-use">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use the information you provide only for the following purposes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>To schedule, confirm, and manage your cleaning appointments</li>
    <li>To send appointment confirmations, reminders, and follow-ups via phone, SMS, or email</li>
    <li>To send our newsletter and promotional offers <strong>only if you have opted in</strong></li>
    <li>To respond to your questions or support requests</li>
    <li>To maintain our internal client records and improve our service quality</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="highlight">
    <p><strong>📱 About Text Messages (SMS):</strong> By providing your phone number and submitting a booking, you consent to receive appointment-related text messages from Custom Cleaning RVA at the number provided. Message frequency varies. Message and data rates may apply. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> at any time to opt out. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for assistance.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="highlight">
    <p><strong>✉️ About Emails / Newsletter:</strong> By checking the newsletter opt-in box on our booking or contact form, you consent to receive marketing emails from Custom Cleaning RVA. You may unsubscribe at any time by clicking "Unsubscribe" in any email or contacting us directly. We process unsubscribe requests within 5 business days.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="sharing">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not sell, rent, or trade</strong> your personal information to any third party.</p>
  <p>We may share your information only in the following limited circumstances:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Our cleaning staff</strong> — cleaners receive the address and appointment details necessary to complete your service</li>
    <li><strong>Service providers</strong> — we may use tools like scheduling software, email platforms, or payment processors that have access to your data only to provide their services to us, under strict confidentiality</li>
    <li><strong>Legal requirements</strong> — if required by law, court order, or to protect the rights and safety of our clients, staff, or the public</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="security">5. How We Protect Your Information</h2>
  <p>We take the security of your personal information seriously. We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your data, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Secure, password-protected internal records systems</li>
    <li>Limiting access to client data to only necessary staff</li>
    <li>Using encrypted communication channels for sensitive information</li>
  </ul>
  <p>No method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. If you have concerns about a specific data security issue, please contact us immediately.</p>

  <h2 id="retention">6. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain your personal information for as long as you are an active client and for a reasonable period afterward for record-keeping purposes. If you would like your data deleted, please contact us and we will remove your records within 30 days, except where retention is required by law.</p>

  <h2 id="your-rights">7. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Access</strong> — Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
    <li><strong>Correction</strong> — Ask us to update inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
    <li><strong>Deletion</strong> — Request that we delete your personal information</li>
    <li><strong>Opt-Out of SMS</strong> — Reply STOP to any text message from us</li>
    <li><strong>Opt-Out of Email</strong> — Click "Unsubscribe" in any email or contact us directly</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:customcleaningrva@gmail.com">customcleaningrva@gmail.com</a>.</p>

  <h2 id="children">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Our services and website are not directed toward children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>

  <h2 id="third-party">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
  <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., Google, social media platforms). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to read their privacy policies.</p>

